# Interview Copilot Feature

## Directory Structure
- `/app/dashboard/interviewCopilot`
  - `page.tsx` - Copilot dashboard
  - `[sessionId]/page.tsx` - Active interview session
  - `components/` - Copilot-specific components
  - `actions/` - Server actions for interview operations
  - `utils/` - Audio processing and AI utilities

